<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="donation.css">
    <title>Donate or Volunteer | Earthcare Initiative</title>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/nmGwm5K/Untitled.png" alt="WebBuilders Logo" width="100" height="100">



        <h1>Earthcare Initiative</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html" style="background-color: #333; color: #fff; padding: 14px 16px; text-decoration: none;">Home Page</a>
            <a href="contactus.html" style="background-color: #333; color: #fff; padding: 14px 16px; text-decoration: none;">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="getinvo.html" style="background-color: #333; color: #fff; padding: 14px 16px; text-decoration: none;">Get Involved</a>
            <a href="donation.html" style="background-color: #333; color: #fff; padding: 14px 16px; text-decoration: none;">Donate</a>
        </nav>

    </header>


    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Donate</h2>
            <p>Your donation helps us continue our mission of promoting sustainability and protecting the environment. Choose an amount to donate:</p>
            <form>
                <label for="amount">$</label>
                <input type="number" id="amount" name="amount" min="1" step="1">
                <button type="submit">Donate Now</button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Volunteer</h2>
            <p>Become a volunteer and help us make a difference in your community. Fill out the form belowto get started:</p>
            <form>
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
                <br>
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email">
                <br>
                <label for="interest">Interest:</label>
                <select id="interest" name="interest">
                    <option value="conservation">IDK</option>
                    <option value="education">IDK</option>
                    <option value="outreach">IDK</option>
                </select>
                <br>
                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Earthcare Initiative. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>